<item>
            <title>[SPARK-2152] the error of comput rightNodeAgg about  Decision tree algorithm  in Spark MLlib </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-2152</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; the error of comput rightNodeAgg about  Decision tree algorithm  in Spark MLlib  about  the function extractLeftRightNodeAggregates() ,when compute rightNodeAgg  used bindata index is error. in the DecisionTree.scala file about  Line 980:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;             rightNodeAgg(featureIndex)(2 * (numBins - 2 - splitIndex)) =&lt;br/&gt;
                binData(shift + (2 * (numBins - 2 - splitIndex))) +&lt;br/&gt;
                  rightNodeAgg(featureIndex)(2 * (numBins - 1 - splitIndex))    &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; the   binData(shift + (2 * (numBins - 2 - splitIndex)))  index compute is error, so the result of rightNodeAgg  include  repeated data about &quot;bins&quot;  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;windows7 ,32 operator,and 3G mem&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
